        "### Step 1: Install Tesseract OCR and PyTesseract\n",
        "\n",
        "First, we need to install Tesseract OCR, which is an open-source OCR engine, and `pytesseract`, which is a Python wrapper for Tesseract. In Google Colab, we can install system packages using `apt-get` and Python packages using `pip`."
      ]
    },
    {
