      "metadata": {
        "id": "81cf15ae"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Step 2: Import Libraries and Upload Image\n",
        "\n",
        "Next, we'll import the necessary libraries and provide a way for you to upload the image file you want to process. Make sure to upload an image containing text."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
